data.description: Build your dream home on this 6.8 acre estate lot inside McMullen Cove's exclusive mountaintop Watson Grande development. This lot has gorgeous views and adjoins roughly 20 acres of community property that won't be developed, providing outstanding privacy and seclusion. Work with the builder of your choice on designing your custom home! The property grants the owner access to the McMullen Cove pool, tennis, miles of walking trails, access to the Flint River and other amenities included in membership to the McMullen Cove Owner Association.
